OL,3,C'It's knocked us for six': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son after boxer's death
OL,6,FRicky Hatton's son Campbell has spoken
OL,7,Fexclusively to our sports
OL,8,Fcorrespondent Mike Hall.
OL,10,FRicky Hatton's son Campbell says his
OL,11,Ffamily have been "hit for six" and
OL,12,Fleft "heartbroken" by his father's
OL,13,Fsudden death.
OL,15,FBut Campbell, who is 24 and a former
OL,16,Fprofessional boxer himself, also said
OL,17,Fthe Hatton family had been overwhelmed
OL,18,Fby what he called the "outpouring of
OL,19,Fsupport" from the public since his
OL,20,Ffather died, aged 46.
