OL,3,C'It's knocked us for six': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son after boxer's death
OL,6,FFormer two-weight world boxing
OL,7,Fchampion Ricky Hatton was found dead
OL,8,Fat his home in Hyde on 14 September.
OL,9,FNo cause of his death has yet been
OL,10,Fannounced.
OL,12,FIn an exclusive interview with Granada
OL,13,FReports sports correspondent Mike
OL,14,FHall, Campbell said of his father's
OL,15,Fpassing: "We are absolutely
OL,16,Fheartbroken...it was so unexpected..
OL,18,F"We had so many plans coming up, so it
OL,19,Fhas knocked us for six, but obviously
OL,20,Fwe are trying to be there for each
OL,21,Fother.
