OL,3,C'It's knocked us for six': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son after boxer's death
OL,6,F"The outpouring of support from
OL,7,Fabsolutely everyone has been amazing,
OL,8,Fso that's helping us through a lot,
OL,9,Fbut yes, (we are) absolutely
OL,10,Fheartbroken."
OL,12,FOf his relationship with his dad,
OL,13,FCampbell, who bears a striking
OL,14,Fresemblance to him, said: "He used to
OL,15,Fcall me his little Mini-Me.
OL,17,F"We were identical in so many ways,
OL,18,Fand I think it's shown through how
OL,19,Fclose we were and the banter we had
OL,20,Fwith each other.
