OL,3,C'It's knocked us for six': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son after boxer's death
OL,6,F"To so many he was Ricky Hatton the
OL,7,Fboxer, but to me he was just my dad,
OL,8,Fand to the family, it was Richard. We
OL,9,Fjust can't get our heads round it at
OL,10,Fthe minute."
OL,12,FHe said the family had been getting
OL,13,Fsome comfort from watching video clips
OL,14,Fof his father's life on social medial,
OL,15,Fshowing his boxing achievements and
OL,16,Falso his sense of humour.
