OL,3,C'It's knocked us for six': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son after boxer's death
OL,6,FHe said both he and his dad were
OL,7,F"diehard" Manchester City fans, and
OL,8,Fthat he was grateful to the club for
OL,9,Fallowing Ricky's daughters, Fearne and
OL,10,FMillie, plus his niece Lola and grand-
OL,11,Fdaughter Lyla, to be mascots for the
OL,12,Frecent match at the Etihad stadium
OL,13,Fagainst Burnley.
OL,15,FAnd as they were both "diehard" Oasis
OL,16,Ffans too, he also thanked the band for
OL,17,Ftheir "Live Forever" tribute to his
OL,18,Fdad during one of their Wembley gigs.
