OL,3,C'It's knocked us for six': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son after boxer's death
OL,6,FAsked if he wanted a large turnout for
OL,7,Fhis dad's funeral, Campbell said:
OL,8,F"That's exactly what he would have
OL,9,Fwanted. He sees his biggest
OL,10,Fachievement as his fanbase, and that's
OL,11,Fwhat he was most proud of.
OL,13,F"So what he'd want would be the
OL,14,Fstreets to be full of people...because
OL,15,Feverything he did, he did for his
OL,16,Ffans."JRicky Hatton's funeral will be
OL,17,Fheld on Friday 10 October at
OL,18,FManchester Cathedral.
